sorcer.service

Interface Contexter<T>

  • All Superinterfaces:
    java.rmi.Remote
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    Context<T>, StrategyContext
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    ArrayContext, ContextResult, ControlContext, CustomContext, DataContext, ListContext, MapContext, PositionalContext, ProcModel, ProviderSession, ScopeContext, ServiceContext, SharedAssociativeContext, SharedIndexedContext, SrvModel

    public interface Contexter<T>
extends java.rmi.Remote
    A service interface related to Context evaluation/invocation and accessing contexts of of context service providers. A context provider that can federate with relevant service providers to provide associative data in the network.
